Audio Format
    https://www.gyan.dev/ffmpeg/builds/#release-builds
    Use ffmpeg to change the audio mode to meet the audio format of Baidu speech recognition.
    We uniformly convert the audio format to wav
    and the format is:
    Codec: PCM_S16LE
    Audio channel: mono (1.0)
    Frequency: 16000 Hz (8000 is fine)

API:
    Using Baidu Short Speech Recognition Standard Edition API, Mandarin Chinese
    Free quota until the end of September
    Total 150,000 times, concurrent 5
